{"tid":1461723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(金融攬炒)請索羅斯出山沽空港元","createTime":"2019-08-13T09:05:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T10:33:56.000Z","uid":72431,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"dd37a3d1bc858e7b34352e7b34ac053d6b38910b","tid":1461723,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:05:44.000Z","msg":"Email比wall street 各大金融大鱷<br />\n請求聯手沽空港元<br />\n唔好理係咪太天真 ,做左無壞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n求英文達人出tempate letter<br />\n求bba撚 揾哂wall street fund email<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1997:<br />\n更為港人所熟知的是，索羅斯是那個在97年帶來亞洲金融風暴，在98年狙擊港元的「金融大鱷」。在這場金融戰爭中，索羅斯以一人之力拖跨了泰國、馬來西亞、印尼、南韓等國家的貨幣和經濟，使這些國家陷入經濟衰退。而在與香港政府一戰中，剛成立的特區政府打下了為國際分析家津津樂道的「勝仗」，成功保衛聯繫匯率和擊退炒家<br />\n<br />\n(之前po過一次,再po無人理就算)"},{"pid":"302be13bba779d79fec59adf02bfaf5a23c05c74","tid":1461723,"uid":282624,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:09:04.000Z","msg":"唔天真<br />\n若港元再現危機沽空一樣賺到笑<br />\n大家幫手襟錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbc191354f2426248979b9683583cd1331e080ad","tid":1461723,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:19:44.000Z","msg":"712"},{"pid":"0576527ad03706f4b8b06dce238b7f96e946f431","tid":1461723,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:18:17.000Z","msg":"712"},{"pid":"36ced7808d27908f87fc21d74398c0fb0dc4b73a","tid":1461723,"uid":171326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T11:05:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e73b2e8942fd2f3e848943b25ee4b40c37d69c43","tid":1461723,"uid":110125,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T11:10:45.000Z","msg":"以前就話有外滙儲備頂得住，依家射哂上大陸。大䲔一出手就收香港皮"},{"pid":"9527bf64dde64bebb7032025f2c0248d80fe817c","tid":1461723,"uid":226955,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T11:12:19.000Z","msg":"趁索羅斯仲未死，快啲叫佢完成埋呢個畢生未竟之志"},{"pid":"64023beb41981d9bddc99989ffe23eb9771de3d6","tid":1461723,"uid":148987,"like":8,"d